love hat pierre heres story your mother about my father lived taiwan several years became fluent mandarin he was good native speakers after hearing him on phone were surprised they found he was white person from us he visited china he was his s wore generic baseball cap cover his bald head he was touring certain site another tourist from country which shall remain unnamed started ragging him about hat wouldnt let up my dad who was mildmannered wasnt quick with comebacks just felt humiliated still get mad think about someone doing my dad think one of beautiful things about travel must be experiencing now learning truth of adage quotdont judge book by its coverquot this other tourist must have pegged my father as just another quotugly americanquot nothing could have been further from truth were he alive today doubt hed be here states watching our democracy crumble hed probably be doing what youre doing keep wearing your hat honor of my dad celebrate quotviva la differencelove vlogs im bit old decrepit now myself most of my travel vicarious are making look like much fun thank very much taking time share your journey with us
